data.name: ZipConstants
desc: defines the constants used by the ZIP interfaces.

items.name: DEFLATED
lines: Compression method for the deflate algorithm (the only one currently supported).

items.name: NO_COMPRESSION
lines: Compression level for no compression.

items.name: BEST_SPEED
lines: Compression level for fastest compression.

items.name: BEST_COMPRESSION
lines: Compression level for best compression.

items.name: DEFAULT_COMPRESSION
lines: Default compression level.

items.name: FILTERED
lines: Compression strategy best used for data consisting mostly of small values with a somewhat random distribution.
Forces more Huffman coding and less string matching.

items.name: HUFFMAN_ONLY
lines: Compression strategy for Huffman coding only.

items.name: DEFAULT_STRATEGY
lines: Default compression strategy.

items.name: STORED
lines: entry is uncompressed

items.name: DEF_MEM_LEVEL
lines: entry is uncompressed
